28:18.030 --> 28:20.783
Resist, but it always ends
the same way with torture.

28:20.800 --> 28:21.983
What way is that?

28:22.000 --> 28:23.558
Everyone breaks.

28:30.500 --> 28:31.990
Du_nn:
Sir,

28:32.010 --> 28:33.807
General mark osborne
in charge

28:33.810 --> 28:35.129
Of an advanced _
weapons systems unit.

28:35.140 --> 28:37.199
Location unknown
as of an hour ago.

28:37.210 --> 28:38.871
The general a dad at ballard?

28:38.880 --> 28:40.848
No, we think he's the target.
Let's find the general

28:40.850 --> 28:44.217
Before the kidnapper gets a hold
of any advanced weapons systems.

28:44.220 --> 28:45.642
We're tracking his phone.

28:45.650 --> 28:47.015
It's a military-secure
blackberry.

28:47.020 --> 28:48.180
You'll need a court order.

28:48.190 --> 28:50.658
Picked one up
at the white house.

28:50.660 --> 28:53.185
Fbi is tracking osborne's phone.

28:53.190 --> 28:54.919
You gave froy and beckwith
burner phones,

28:54.930 --> 28:56.989
But not the general;
he's still got his own phone?

28:57.000 --> 28:59.150
Those feds got ahead of me.

28:59.170 --> 29:02.059
I didn't expect that they'd
figure the general was my target

29:02.070 --> 29:04.834
Until it was over.

29:04.840 --> 29:07.001
Those feds don't stop.

29:07.010 --> 29:10.229
Clone the general's
number, please.

29:10.240 --> 29:11.229
Ten more seconds, sir.

29:11.250 --> 29:13.605
(beeping)

29:14.920 --> 29:16.740
Copy the clone,
project the copies.

29:19.890 --> 29:21.881
That's it.

29:21.890 --> 29:23.255
That's the general's phone.

29:23.260 --> 29:25.319
(rapid beeping)

29:27.690 --> 29:28.884
He's projecting
cloned copies.

29:28.900 --> 29:30.197
The kidnapper is messing

29:30.200 --> 29:31.929
With us right now in real time.

29:31.930 --> 29:33.363
They're all diversions,

29:33.370 --> 29:35.725
But we need to check
all these locations now.

29:35.740 --> 29:37.935
We'll take that one.

29:37.940 --> 29:39.965
It's the kingsley grand.

29:39.970 --> 29:41.631
Tha_t hotel has
a preSIdential swte.

29:41.640 --> 29:42.971
It's a secure location

29:42.980 --> 29:44.800
The white house chief of staff
has access to.

29:48.780 --> 29:51.715
What if we stop the parents
from doing as they're told,

29:51.720 --> 29:53.483
And the kidnapper kills a kid?
VVhatthen?

29:53.490 --> 29:54.980
I guess that depends on what

29:54.990 --> 29:56.457
We're stopping the parents
from doing.

30:01.490 --> 30:04.129
Where's mr. BecloNith?
He's meeting the
general at the hotel.

30:07.630 --> 30:10.633
Where's mr. Froy?
He took the bag up
to the hotel suite.

30:10.640 --> 30:12.631
We don't have a
video feed in there,

30:12.640 --> 30:15.006
But he should be
waiting for your call.

30:30.520 --> 30:33.023
(phone rings)

30:33.030 --> 30:34.782
Francis (distorted):
Mr. Beckwith give you the bag?

30:34.800 --> 30:36.654
Yes.

30:36.660 --> 30:38.594
(sighs)
what do you want with me?

30:38.600 --> 30:40.158
Five years ago,
you were shot down

30:40.170 --> 30:42.092
And tortured for three weeks

30:42.100 --> 30:43.590
Before you were rescued.

30:43.600 --> 30:45.033
That was horrible.

30:45.040 --> 30:46.701
Why are you telling me this now?

30:46.710 --> 30:47.961
Use the key.

30:47.980 --> 30:49.163
Open the bag now.

30:54.010 --> 30:55.500
(lock clattering)

31:02.160 --> 31:04.515
Mr. Froy?

31:05.860 --> 31:08.328
Do to the general
what was done to you.

31:08.330 --> 31:10.491
Make something of that horror.

31:10.500 --> 31:12.559
Please...

31:14.170 --> 31:16.161
I-I'll do anything else.

31:16.170 --> 31:18.331
I don't need you
to do anything else.

31:18.340 --> 31:19.864
I need you to do this.

31:19.870 --> 31:21.929
(door opens)

31:31.680 --> 31:32.840
Who the hell are you?

31:32.850 --> 31:34.715
What the hell's
going on here?

31:45.000 --> 31:47.195
Five blocks.

31:47.200 --> 31:48.827
We run for it.

31:59.710 --> 32:01.678
I get what you want
with osborne.

32:01.680 --> 32:03.773
What I don't get
is the five-star hotel.

32:03.780 --> 32:06.248
The presidential suite
would arouse no suspicion

32:06.250 --> 32:09.117
In the general,
and it's soundproof.

32:12.090 --> 32:15.025
This is insane!

32:15.030 --> 32:17.590
That man is a friend of mine!
We went to school together!

32:17.600 --> 32:18.851
Froy:
Don't think about it.

32:18.870 --> 32:20.690
Put your mind somewhere else.
It'll help.

32:21.600 --> 32:23.431
Put the earbud in the general.

32:29.040 --> 32:30.200
(grunting)

32:30.210 --> 32:31.336
(panting):
Sorry. Sorry.

32:36.050 --> 32:37.711
Can you see that light?

32:39.890 --> 32:41.414
Yes.
When it's green,

32:41.420 --> 32:44.253
Use the cables on him.
When it's red, stop.

32:44.260 --> 32:47.127
You and mr. Beckwith put those
headphones on now.

32:47.130 --> 32:49.325
Then remove the tape.

32:49.330 --> 32:51.059
That way, you can't hear
what the general's saying.

32:51.070 --> 32:53.789
You don't need
to know any of that.

32:58.940 --> 33:00.305
Can you hear me, general?

33:01.770 --> 33:03.909
I'm going to ask you
a few questions

33:03.910 --> 33:05.138
About operation lenox.

33:05.150 --> 33:06.344
Who the hell is this?

33:06.350 --> 33:07.977
See that man in front of you?

33:07.980 --> 33:10.016
He wants his daughter back.

33:10.020 --> 33:12.671
How far do you think
he'll go to do that?

33:12.690 --> 33:14.908
Operation lenox, there was
a massacre. People died.

33:14.920 --> 33:16.751
I need proof of that.

33:16.760 --> 33:17.818
Where can I find it?

33:17.830 --> 33:19.479
I don't know

33:19.490 --> 33:20.923
What you're talking about.

33:37.440 --> 33:38.771
No...

33:40.510 --> 33:42.068
(gasping)

33:54.490 --> 33:56.720
I need you to make a call.

33:56.730 --> 33:58.197
I've been here before.

33:58.200 --> 34:00.191
The top floor is
the presidential suite.

34:00.200 --> 34:02.225
Like a bunker.
Let's check in at security.

34:02.240 --> 34:03.992
I am in the lobby right now.

34:04.000 --> 34:06.059
There is a black man with a gun.

34:06.070 --> 34:07.799
Oh, god.

34:07.810 --> 34:10.005
I don't know what to do.

34:10.010 --> 34:12.877
We need help in the lobby.

34:18.180 --> 34:20.910
(pained screaming)

34:20.920 --> 34:21.989
(sizzling)

34:21.990 --> 34:23.719
(groans)

34:26.160 --> 34:27.582
When that light goes green,

34:27.590 --> 34:30.354
He will begin again
and he will not stop.

34:30.360 --> 34:32.851
He loves his daughter more
than he hates this.

34:32.870 --> 34:34.861
And he knows now
how to get her back.

34:34.870 --> 34:37.191
He just has to keep hurting you.

34:37.200 --> 34:38.667
Again: Operation lenox.

34:38.670 --> 34:40.160
Where do I find proof?

34:40.170 --> 34:42.263
I don't know that name.

34:42.280 --> 34:44.236
Those were your men.
You chose them.

34:44.240 --> 34:45.878
There was a massacre.
People died.

34:45.880 --> 34:47.279
Where can I find proof?

34:47.280 --> 34:50.169
How do you know that?

34:50.180 --> 34:51.875
Gibson.

34:51.890 --> 34:53.448
You're francis gibson.

34:53.450 --> 34:55.213
No.

34:55.220 --> 34:57.609
But when we broke gibson,
he gave you up.

34:57.620 --> 34:59.110
Where is the proof?

34:59.130 --> 35:01.257
There is no proof.

35:01.260 --> 35:03.251
What you want does not exist.

35:08.530 --> 35:10.737
This gets my kid back.
This gets my kid back.

35:10.740 --> 35:12.037
This gets my kid back.

35:12.040 --> 35:13.860
(groans)

35:17.980 --> 35:19.800
(screams)

35:19.810 --> 35:21.869
I'm secret service.

35:21.880 --> 35:23.518
Fbi. I'm gonna go
for my badge.

35:26.750 --> 35:28.980
Sorry. We got a call.

35:28.990 --> 35:30.116
What did that call say?

35:30.120 --> 35:31.417
Man with a gun in the lobby.

35:31.430 --> 35:32.613
The kidnapper knows we're here.

35:32.630 --> 35:33.654
Then we're in the right place.

35:33.660 --> 35:35.059
I'm gonna call for backup.

35:35.060 --> 35:37.790
I need the secure key
for that suite.

35:37.800 --> 35:39.620
(screams)

35:39.630 --> 35:41.359
(gasping)

35:45.440 --> 35:46.907
To make sure
he keeps doing this.

35:46.910 --> 35:48.502
I know you want your son, but...

35:48.510 --> 35:51.070
You can stop this. Stop him.

35:52.110 --> 35:53.646
Look at the light, general.

35:53.650 --> 35:55.641
(groans)

36:03.520 --> 36:05.511
No. No!

36:05.530 --> 36:08.249
No,no,no!
The proof of the massacre

36:08.260 --> 36:10.990
By those soldiers
is on a helmet cam video.

36:11.000 --> 36:12.353
Where is that video?

36:14.000 --> 36:15.092
Vault 48...

36:15.100 --> 36:16.636
Cia, main building.

36:16.640 --> 36:18.596
Authenticate it.
State your name.

36:18.610 --> 36:22.137
Mark osborne.

36:22.140 --> 36:24.779
General, US. Army.

36:30.020 --> 36:32.511
(sighs) oh, god!

36:32.520 --> 36:34.579
(gasping)

36:37.660 --> 36:38.854
Sorry, mark.

36:38.860 --> 36:40.122
I had no choice.

36:40.130 --> 36:41.483
They were gonna
kill my kid.

36:41.500 --> 36:42.728
It's okay, frank.

36:42.730 --> 36:44.357
It's okay. I understand.

36:44.360 --> 36:47.295
But he's gonna kill me,
you know that, right?

36:47.300 --> 36:49.564
He's gonna make you kill me.

36:50.970 --> 36:52.767
You gotta untie me.

37:04.350 --> 37:06.147
What did you do?

37:06.150 --> 37:08.289
My turn to ask
the questions.

37:10.160 --> 37:11.479
What do you know
about the kidnapper?

37:11.490 --> 37:12.809
Nothing!

37:14.190 --> 37:15.555
Mark, what the hell
are you doing?!

37:15.560 --> 37:17.858
I'm shooting him
until he dies,

37:17.860 --> 37:19.396
And then I'm gonna start
on you, frank.

37:19.400 --> 37:20.719
What do you know
about the kidnapper?

37:20.730 --> 37:22.368
I don't know anything.

37:22.370 --> 37:23.997
(groaning)

37:24.000 --> 37:25.865
Federal agents!

37:25.870 --> 37:28.430
Federal agents!

37:29.410 --> 37:30.570
General mark osborne?

37:30.580 --> 37:32.207
Yes.

37:32.210 --> 37:34.007
We're here to help you.

37:42.390 --> 37:43.414
That man needs
medical attention.

37:43.420 --> 37:44.853
You need to put
the gun down.

37:44.860 --> 37:47.556
They were gonna kill me.
I had to shoot him.

37:47.560 --> 37:49.221
That's not what happened.
That's not why you shot him!

37:49.230 --> 37:50.527
They were gonna kill me.

37:50.530 --> 37:51.758
We can figure
all that out later,

37:51.770 --> 37:54.364
But right now, put the gun down.

37:54.370 --> 37:57.737
Francis (distorted):
General, they're here
to help you.

37:57.740 --> 37:58.968
Put the gun down.

37:58.970 --> 38:01.109
Go on.
Finley:
General...

38:01.110 --> 38:03.271
You've been through a lot, and
you're not thinking straight.

38:04.580 --> 38:06.229
Just put the gun down
so we can help.

38:06.250 --> 38:07.899
Let them help you.

38:07.910 --> 38:09.775
Let them take you out of here.

38:09.780 --> 38:12.544
To the court-martial
that waits for you.

38:12.550 --> 38:15.087
To your family
turning away from you.

38:15.090 --> 38:18.912
Your children think
you're a patriot.

38:18.930 --> 38:22.320
But you're not.
You're a criminal, a murderer.

38:22.330 --> 38:26.255
Let those agents help you out
of here so you can face that.

38:26.270 --> 38:28.158
Finley:
Put the gun down!

38:28.170 --> 38:30.468
That man is gonna die
if we don't get him help.

38:30.470 --> 38:32.438
Let us help you here.

38:32.440 --> 38:34.101
It's_all out there
waiting for you.

38:34.110 --> 38:37.170
Shame, humiliation,

38:37.180 --> 38:38.602
The truth.

38:38.610 --> 38:41.147
And something else.
Do you know what?

38:41.150 --> 38:42.742
What?

38:42.750 --> 38:44.172
What else?

38:44.180 --> 38:45.340
Who are you talking to?

38:45.350 --> 38:46.749
Who's he talking
to, finley?

38:46.750 --> 38:48.286
What else waits for me?

38:48.290 --> 38:49.917
Put the gun down now!

38:49.920 --> 38:51.911
A cia bullet.

38:51.930 --> 38:55.422
There's no way they're
ever letting you testify.

38:56.800 --> 38:58.449
Oh, god, he's right.

38:58.470 --> 38:59.528
He's talking to the kidnapper.

38:59.530 --> 39:01.259
No! No!

39:01.270 --> 39:02.828
(gunshot)

39:05.200 --> 39:07.703
Wipe all trace of this call.

39:09.180 --> 39:11.375
What did general osborne
tell the kidnappers?

39:11.380 --> 39:12.506
I don't know.

39:12.510 --> 39:14.341
What questions did they ask him?

39:14.350 --> 39:15.772
I don't know.

39:15.780 --> 39:18.544
You were in the room
the entire time

39:18.550 --> 39:20.711
Your friend was being tortured.

39:20.720 --> 39:22.381
I couldn't hear anything.

39:22.390 --> 39:24.984
Not a word.

39:24.990 --> 39:26.787
We just wanted our kids back.

39:26.790 --> 39:28.849
I asked what
we were gonna do.

39:30.630 --> 39:35.067
And that voice said,
"truth and pain."

39:36.340 --> 39:38.069
Isn't that what happened?

39:39.370 --> 39:41.804
Don't I get my kid back now?

39:49.820 --> 39:52.812
Where are we?

39:52.820 --> 39:56.950
We... We were at the
mansion, and then...

40:15.370 --> 40:18.407
Dad! Dad!

40:30.390 --> 40:31.550
The kidnapper used
those parents

40:31.560 --> 40:33.209
To torture general osborne,

40:33.230 --> 40:35.881
And the general gave up
something he couldn't live with.

40:35.900 --> 40:37.356
The equipment they brought
into that room,

40:37.360 --> 40:38.554
We got nothing off it?

40:38.570 --> 40:39.923
Nothing.

40:39.930 --> 40:41.397
No prints. No trace
back to anywhere.

40:41.400 --> 40:42.560
Who are these people?

40:42.570 --> 40:43.935
We found an earbud

40:43.940 --> 40:45.430
In the general's ear.

40:45.440 --> 40:47.408
Kidnapper was talking
to him the whole time.

40:47.410 --> 40:49.059
What does that tell you?

40:49.080 --> 40:50.729
The kidnapper was
in the general's head

40:50.740 --> 40:52.776
When he killed himself.

40:52.780 --> 40:54.543
This was personal.

41:00.490 --> 41:02.549
It will be terrible
for the general's family

41:02.560 --> 41:03.754
After all this is over

41:03.760 --> 41:05.751
To find out why
he killed himself,

41:05.760 --> 41:07.751
The terrible things he did.

41:07.760 --> 41:09.648
They all looked up to him.

41:09.660 --> 41:12.629
It'll crush them to find out
what kind of man he really was.

41:12.630 --> 41:16.589
You know, it's one thing hacking
into the white house telecom,

41:16.600 --> 41:18.989
But that massacre video
you need,

41:19.010 --> 41:21.934
It's locked inside a cia vault.

41:21.940 --> 41:23.669
How you planning
on getting it out?

41:36.460 --> 41:38.519
Let's place the next call.

